'''多梳家族蛋白'''（{{lang-en|Polycomb-group proteins}}）是在果蝇中首次发现的能够重塑[[染色质|染色质]]从而使[[基因|基因]]在[[表观遗传|表观遗传]]上沉默的一类[[蛋白质家族|蛋白质家族]]。多梳家族蛋白因其可在[[黑腹果蝇|黑腹果蝇]]的[[胚胎發育|胚胎發育]]过程中通过调整染色质结构沉默[[同源异形基因|同源异形基因]]而著名<ref name= Portoso >{{cite book | chapterurl = http://books.google.com/books?id=r67Lrf9r9XEC&pg=PA29 | author = Portoso M, Cavalli G | editor = Morris KV | year = 2008 | chapter = The Role of RNAi and Noncoding RNAs in Polycomb Mediated Control of Gene Expression and Genomic Programming | title = RNA and the Regulation of Gene Expression: A Hidden Layer of Complexity | publisher = Caister Academic Press | isbn = 978-1-904455-25-7 | pages = 29–44 | access-date = 2013-11-03 | archive-date = 2014-01-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102023229/http://books.google.com/books?id=r67Lrf9r9XEC&pg=PA29 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 昆虫中 ==
{{le|果蝇属|Drosophila}}的{{le|三胸家族蛋白|Trithorax-group proteins|三胸家族}}（trxG）与多梳家族（PcG）蛋白的作用是相互拮抗的，他们都与被称为{{le|细胞记忆模块|Cellular Memory Modules}}（CMMs）的染色体元件发生相互作用。三胸家族（trxG）蛋白维持着基因表达的活性状态，多梳家族（PcG）蛋白通过抑制染色体活性而对冲这种激活作用，这种抑制功能在多个细胞世代中一直保持稳定，只能通过生殖细胞分化过程才能得到逆转。多梳基因复合物所介导的沉默至少需要三类多蛋白复合物：PRC1（多梳抑制复合物1）、[[PRC2|PRC2]]与[[PhoRC|PhoRC]]。这些复合物共同作用才能达到抑制的效果。

== 哺乳动物中 ==
多梳家族的基因表达在哺乳动物中对发育的多个方面有着重要作用<ref>{{cite journal | author=Ku M, Koche RP, Rheinbay E, Mendenhall EM, Endoh M, Mikkelsen TS, Presser A, Nusbaum C, Xie X, Chi AS, Adli M, Kasif S, Ptaszek LM, Cowan CA, Lander ES, Koseki H, Bernstein BE | title=Genomewide analysis of PRC1 and PRC2 occupancy identifies two classes of bivalent domains | journal=[[PLOS_Genetics|PLOS Genetics]] | volume=4 | issue=10 | year=2008 | pages=e1000242 | url=http://www.plosgenetics.org/article/info%3Adoi%2F10.1371%2Fjournal.pgen.1000242 | doi=10.1371/journal.pgen.1000242 | id= | pmid=18974828 | access-date=2013-11-03 | archive-date=2015-01-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150111063625/http://www.plosgenetics.org/article/info:doi/10.1371/journal.pgen.1000242 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[BMI1|Bmi1]]多梳[[RING指结构域|RING指结构域]]蛋白促使神经干细胞自我更新<ref name=pmid15964994>{{cite journal | author=Molofsky AV, He S, Bydon M, Morrison SJ, Pardal R | title=Bmi-1 promotes neural stem cell self-renewal and neural development but not mouse growth and survival by repressing the p16Ink4a and p19Arf senescence pathways | journal=[[Genes_&_Development|Genes & Development]] | volume=19 | issue=12 | year=2005 | pages=1432–1437 | url=http://genesdev.cshlp.org/content/19/12/1432.long | pmid=15964994 | doi=10.1101/gad.1299505 | pmc=1151659 | access-date=2013-11-03 | archive-date=2021-05-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210525174135/http://genesdev.cshlp.org/content/19/12/1432.long | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=pmid14722607>{{cite journal | author=Park IK, Morrison SJ, Clarke MF | title=Bmi1, stem cells, and senescence regulation | journal=[[Journal_of_Clinical_Investigation|Journal of Clinical Investigation]] | volume=113 | issue=2 | year=2004 | pages=175-179 | url=http://www.jci.org/articles/view/20800 | pmid=14722607 | pmc=311443 | doi=10.1172/JCI20800 | access-date=2013-11-03 | archive-date=2020-07-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728120446/https://www.jci.org/articles/view/20800 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。鼠科PRC2基因的无效突变体会导致胚胎死亡，但大多数PRC1的突变体则生下来就是同源异形突变体，后者导致围生期死亡。相反的是PcG蛋白过表达会与多种肿瘤的严重程度和侵袭力成正相关<ref name="pmid18447587">{{cite journal | author = Sauvageau M, Sauvageau G | title = Polycomb group genes: keeping stem cell activity in balance | journal = PLoS Biol. | volume = 6 | issue = 4 | pages = e113 | pmid = 18447587 | pmc = 2689701 | doi = 10.1371/journal.pbio.0060113 |date=April 2008}}</ref>。哺乳动物的PRC1核心复合物与果蝇的非常相似。已知多梳Bmi1可调[[ARF抑癌基因|''ink4''基因座]]（''p16''<sup>Ink4a</sup>和''p19''<sup>Arf</sup>）<ref name="pmid15964994" /><ref name=pmid20716961>{{cite journal | author=Popov N, Gil J | title=Epigenetic regulation of the INK4b-ARF-INK4a locus: in sickness and in health | journal=EPIGENETICS | volume=5 | issue=8 | year=2010 | pages=685-690 | url=http://www.landesbioscience.com/journals/epigenetics/article/12996/?nocache=2141572894 | format=[[PDF|PDF]] | pmid=20716961 | doi=10.4161/epi.5.8.12996 | pmc=3052884 | access-date=2013-11-03 | archive-date=2020-05-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200511085434/https://taylorandfrancis.com/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 植物中 ==
[[File:DEV035048A.jpg|缩略图]]
PcG蛋白FIE在{{le|小立碗藓|Physcomitrella patens}}中特异性表达于如未受精[[卵细胞|卵细胞]]等的[[干细胞|干细胞]]中，这一点通过组织化学[[GUS报道系统|GUS染色]]后显示出的蓝色进行识别。在受精后的早期[[胚胎|胚胎]]''FIE''基因很快失活<ref name="pmid19542356">{{cite journal | author = Mosquna A, Katz A, Decker EL, Rensing SA, Reski R, Ohad N | title = Regulation of stem cell maintenance by the Polyclmb protein FIE has been conserved during land plant evolution | journal = Development | volume = 136 | issue = 14 | pages = 2433–44 | pmid = 19542356 | doi = 10.1242/dev.035048  |date=July 2009}}</ref><ref>The Polycomb gene FIE is expressed (blue) in unfertilised egg cells of the moss Physcomitrella patens (right) and expression ceases after fertilisation in the developing diploid sporophyte (left). In situ GUS staining of two female sex organs (archegonia) of a transgenic plant expressing a translational fusion of FIE-uidA under control of the native FIE promoter. {{cite web |url=http://dev.biologists.org/content/vol136/issue14/cover.shtml |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-07-03 |archive-date=2009-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090626214348/http://dev.biologists.org/content/vol136/issue14/cover.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

对于哺乳动物中：保持细胞处于分化状态来说，PcG是必不可少的；植物中则不是这样的：继发地缺失PcG会导致去分化，促进胚胎发育<ref name="pmid19680533">{{cite journal | author = Aichinger E, Villar CB, Farrona S, Reyes JC, Hennig L, Köhler C | title = CHD3 proteins and polycomb group proteins antagonistically determine cell identity in Arabidopsis | journal = PLoS Genet. | volume = 5 | issue = 8 | pages = e1000605 | pmid = 19680533 | pmc = 2718830 | doi = 10.1371/journal.pgen.1000605 |date=August 2009}}</ref>。

多梳家族蛋白通过沉默[[开花基因座C|开花基因座C]]基因而干扰其对开花的控制<ref name="pmid18852898">{{cite journal | author = Jiang D, Wang Y, Wang Y, He Y | title = Repression of FLOWERING LOCUS C and FLOWERING LOCUS T by the Arabidopsis Polycomb repressive complex 2 components | journal = PLoS ONE | volume = 3 | issue = 10 | pages = e3404 | year = 2008 | pmid = 18852898 | pmc = 2561057 | doi = 10.1371/journal.pone.0003404 }}</ref>。开花基因座C基因是植物中抑制开花通路中的关键环节，在冬季该基因是被沉默的，这被认为是干扰植物[[春化现象|春化现象]]的主要因素<ref name="pmid10716723">{{cite journal | author = Sheldon CC, Rouse DT, Finnegan EJ, Peacock WJ, Dennis ES | title = The molecular basis of vernalization: the central role of FLOWERING LOCUS C (FLC) | journal = Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. U.S.A. | volume = 97 | issue = 7 | pages = 3753–8 | pmid = 10716723 | pmc = 16312 | doi = 10.1073/pnas.060023597 |date=March 2000}}</ref>。

